<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/125720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F125720_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=abd32ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n唔好意思，我之前冇睇其他諗法，都係食食下飯突然有感而發姐。"},{"pid":"55fc7c3c416e58e9ebc830e0d510c381579ba947","tid":92933,"uid":30669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"咁老公仔女上北京做人質個件事呢<br />\n咩玩法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ba6b10738b8074d0a10581fd823f4aef14088a","tid":92933,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁老公仔女上北京做人質個件事呢<br />\n咩玩法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔搵人做人質，邊個肯出黎做大龍鳳"},{"pid":"c0bc90da38440fe86d1eab496c14d9f2befb74c2","tid":92933,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭又發功"},{"pid":"e79955b758f72c4966192cbb6d245678ab2a2fcb","tid":92933,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"中共都唔想搞大個中港矛盾嘅戰意，醒目嘅一定揀薯片佬順一順民心，個兩個傻閪女人仲衰過689"},{"pid":"7751ef479026856a49c36619e6417a0b520cdb12","tid":92933,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中央見香港人咁唔合作，想係今次選舉上面<span style=\"color: red;\">營造「民主」選舉</span>，等香港人以為選出一個香港人會揀既人做特首。<br />\n<br />\n首先，要令人覺得呢個人唔係中央想要既人。(e.g.一個月先批辭職呢d表面功夫)<br />\n<br />\n另外，要有一個中央所揀選既對手。(本身係689，689唔想打場必敗既仗，借勢唔選，所以淋病先要係689唔選之後不得不參選做醜人)<br />\n<br />\n中央唔想任命既人唔係薯片，係